'We were running around the city looking at things and I finally said: 'Well why are you buying?'' Mr Brown said to the Chinese state broadcaster.

'And she said, well, her daughter was going to go to Columbia, or NYU or maybe Harvard and so she needed to be in the centre of the city and that was why she was picking this one particular apartment.

So I said: 'Oh, how old is your daughter?' and she said: 'Well she's two'. And I was just shocked.'

